      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/trivia/work/6851-the-bible-according-to-mark-twain">Trivia About The Bible Accordi...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
